Senior AI is a platform that helps individuals and companies build and manage software in a more productive and secure manner. The AI will understand all of your projects, independently and collectively, unlocking incredible possibilities for faster and more reliable development.

Add Your Codebase

Import your repositories from your GIT hosting service and start interacting with your code. Let Senior AI help and guide you in anything you need.

Entire codebase awareness gives you incredible possibilities for further software development - from bug analysis, specific features requests, security optimization and everything in between.

Enhanced productivity and security

Productivity

Senior AI already understands everything about the product you are building. It can guide the development process, providing code for specific features or requests and ideas perfectly tailored to your codebase without spending time on teaching it all the technical inner workings.

Security

Complex projects have complex bugs and security implications, Senior AI is able to look into them and connect the dots to find the bugs and show a pathway ahead for better security, simultaneously saving time and making your code more secure.
